Scope of this vendoring
-----------------------

Guidance only. The upstream runtime tooling is intentionally omitted to honor
r-stack's zero-runtime-dependency rule:

  - Node.js scripts (scripts/*.mjs)
  - agent configs (agents/*.toml, agents/*.yaml)
  - the `$impeccable` command system, live browser-iteration mode, and hooks

Files reproduced/adapted here under Apache-2.0:

  - SKILL.md          design-guidance sections; runtime scaffolding removed,
                      one model-specific aside generalized
  - reference/brand.md    verbatim, minus one dangling link to an omitted
                          tooling reference (live.md)
  - reference/product.md  verbatim

The remaining upstream reference/ guides (craft, shape, audit, polish, etc.)
are available at the source URL above and may be added later after passing the
skill-security-auditor checklist.

